            New Cutting-Edge Facilities, Diverse Student Body, and Small Class Sizes Characterizes the Rockford Campus Experience
          Heading link



 
Copy link







TOP BENEFITS OF ATTENDING UIC’s HEALTH SCIENCES CAMPUS AT ROCKFORD
 

Competitive in-state tuition for ALL students coupled with a lower cost of living in Rockford
A small class size of 30-35 students where faculty will know your name and you will know all your classmates
An excellent faculty to student ratio where you work with world class faculty
A diverse and inclusive environment; 30% of our first year class are from under represented minority groups
Interprofessional opportunities with students from our Colleges of Medicine and Nursing

Learn how to apply or schedule a visit now!







